sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant AG  as Agente Externo<br/>(test-conference-agent)
    participant MCP as mcp-server-plughub<br/>(external-agent.ts)
    participant RDS as Redis
    participant KFK as Kafka
    participant RE  as Routing Engine<br/>(Python)
    participant BR  as Orchestrator Bridge<br/>(Python)
    participant CG  as Channel Gateway<br/>— ou trigger —

    Note over AG,CG: ── FASE 1: Agente se registra e aguarda ──────────────────────────────────────

    AG->>MCP: wait_for_assignment(session_token, timeout_s=120)

    MCP->>MCP: gera wait_key = "especialista-001:1713356789"
    MCP->>RDS: HSET default:agent:instance:especialista-001<br/>wait_key = "especialista-001:1713356789"

    loop a cada 15s (HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_S)
        MCP->>RDS: BLPOP default:agent:queue:especialista-001 15s<br/>(duplicate connection — não bloqueia outros tools)
        Note right of RDS: timeout → sem contato
        MCP->>KFK: PUBLISH agent.lifecycle<br/>{event:"agent_heartbeat", instance_id, agent_type_id,<br/>pools, status:"ready", ...}
        KFK-->>RE: consome agent_heartbeat
        RE->>RDS: renova TTL da instância (30s)<br/>garante visibilidade no pool
    end

    Note over AG,CG: ── FASE 2: Contato chega ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

    alt Contato normal (cliente conecta via WebSocket)
        CG->>RDS: SETEX session:{id}:meta<br/>{customer_id, channel, tenant_id, ...}  TTL 4h
        CG->>KFK: PUBLISH conversations.inbound<br/>{session_id, tenant_id, pool_id, customer_id, ...}
    else Conferência (trigger agent_join_conference)
        AG->>MCP: agent_join_conference(session_id, agent_type_id, pool_id)
        MCP->>RDS: SET conference:{id}:participant:{pid} (metadata)
        MCP->>RDS: SET session:{id}:conference_id = conference_id
        MCP->>KFK: PUBLISH conversations.inbound<br/>{session_id, pool_id, agent_type_id,<br/>conference_id, channel_identity, ...}
        MCP-->>AG: {conference_id, participant_id, status:"joining"}
    end

    Note over AG,CG: ── FASE 3: Routing Engine roteia ──────────────────────────────────────────────

    KFK-->>RE: consome conversations.inbound
    RE->>RDS: SMEMBERS default:pool:especialista_ia:instances
    Note right of RE: filtra por agent_type_id se presente<br/>(conferência restringe ao tipo declarado)
    RE->>RDS: HGETALL default:agent:instance:especialista-001<br/>verifica: status=ready, current_sessions < max
    RE->>RDS: HMSET default:agent:instance:especialista-001<br/>status=busy, current_sessions++
    RE->>KFK: PUBLISH conversations.routed<br/>{session_id, result:{allocated:true,<br/>instance_id, agent_type_id, pool_id,<br/>conference_id?, channel_identity?}}

    Note over AG,CG: ── FASE 4: Bridge ativa o agente ──────────────────────────────────────────────

    KFK-->>BR: consome conversations.routed
    BR->>BR: result.allocated == True?<br/>framework == "external-mcp"?

    BR->>RDS: HGET default:agent:instance:especialista-001 wait_key
    Note right of RDS: retorna "especialista-001:1713356789"

    BR->>BR: monta context_package =<br/>{session_id, contact_id, tenant_id,<br/>agent_type_id, pool_id, assigned_at,<br/>wait_key: "especialista-001:1713356789",<br/>is_conference, conference_id?,<br/>channel_identity?, participant_id?}

    BR->>RDS: LPUSH default:agent:queue:especialista-001<br/>JSON(context_package)
    BR->>RDS: SADD session:{id}:ai_agents "especialista-001"
    BR->>RDS: SETEX session:{id}:routing:especialista-001<br/>{snapshot da instância para restore no contact_closed}
    BR->>RDS: SETEX session:{id}:pending_queue:especialista-001<br/>JSON(context_package)  TTL 10min<br/>(para LREM se sessão fechar antes do agente consumir)

    Note over AG,CG: ── FASE 5: BLPOP retorna e valida wait_key ───────────────────────────────────

    RDS-->>MCP: BLPOP retorna [queue_key, JSON(context_package)]
    MCP->>MCP: context_package.wait_key == waitKey?
    alt wait_key diverge (item obsoleto de restart anterior)
        Note over MCP: descarta silenciosamente → continue no loop
    else wait_key bate
        MCP-->>AG: return {context_package}
    end

    Note over AG,CG: ── FASE 6: Agente inicia atendimento ─────────────────────────────────────────

    AG->>MCP: agent_busy(session_token, conversation_id=session_id)
    AG->>MCP: send_message(text="Olá! Como posso ajudar?")
    AG->>MCP: wait_for_message(session_id, timeout_s=120, conference_id?)
    Note over AG,MCP: XREADGROUP BLOCK em session:{id}:stream<br/>(duplicate connection — não bloqueia outros tools)
